Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(暑假時正門封閉 請由側門進出)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.88,0:02:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第三話  夏日感傷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}熊本縣的各位聽眾早安\N各位早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}今天看來也會相當的炎熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.99,0:02:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}請各位不要屈服於酷暑跟幻獸 好好打起精神來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}首先就是「每日今天」的專欄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}今天是8月13日 各位知道是什麼日子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}今天是國民義務兵役法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.47,0:02:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}通稱學生徵兵法通過的日子\N(國會通過學生徵兵法)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這麼快就說出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.38,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}21年前 也就是1978年的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.75,0:02:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}國會通過了學生徵兵法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.62,0:02:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}也就是說 至今保護我們的兵役制度是在今天誕生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.59,0:02:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}當時的媒體做出了下列的報導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.66,0:02:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}目前成為國會焦點的國民義務兵役法案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}已經在本日多數表決通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.97,0:03:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}由芝村重工業所開發對幻獸最新人型戰車AMTT-500
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.38,0:03:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}為避免適任駕駛員之成年人口損失過多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.05,0:03:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}並且將適任者保持在一定人數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}朝野黨團至今都為此進行協調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.63,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}經過這次的決議 明年起徵兵年齡限制降為16歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.93,0:03:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}這是為了人類未來而做出的痛苦抉擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.57,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fnsimhei}對於今後的青少年而言…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼要關掉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一大早就看這種節目 心情會不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們平常不都是看這台的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不喜歡裏頭的內容啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼叫做學生徵兵法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧了那玩意 害我寶貴的青春都浪費掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.82,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟有誰會希望在這間破宿舍跟一群大男人一起住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.60,0:03:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也可以在立法之前就放棄兵役 去做其他工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20年前？你開玩笑的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.38,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想想我的不幸 就是從21年前的今天開始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.58,0:04:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本擁有世間罕見俊美的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在應該在大海或深山 跟眾多美女一起享受青春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果還是用你的牢騷結尾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.13,0:04:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剪刀、石頭、布！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是速水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的賭運也太差了吧～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正輸在那種地方也沒什麼好難過的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水他平常雖然倒楣 不過在戰場上倒是很幸運呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神畢竟是公平的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.66,0:05:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我來說好像不是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中或許也有不太公平的神吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-是真的嗎\N-真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.49,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是因為她 所以現在才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種時候 應該在大海或深山享受青春的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟不知道什麼時候要出動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們特別班是沒有暑假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能在不妨礙任務的狀況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.87,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各自調整 休息個幾天而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能問你一件事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.39,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不公平的神是指什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指真紀嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真紀她是個不幸少女喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-田邊你沒事吧\N-我很喜歡這個的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬鈴薯燉肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要是我最喜歡吃的菜 就一定會不小心打翻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒摔壞 碗沒摔壞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣就會摔壞 那田邊可就賠不完咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真紀是世界上最不幸的女生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼啦 太沒精神了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣還算是士兵嗎 還算是5121部隊的駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.98,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說啊 駕駛員需要的是反射神經跟判斷力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟體力應該沒有關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.63,0:07:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HWT操作失靈的話怎麼辦 最後還不是要靠體力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就當作有幻獸在追你們 給我拚命跑吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個健身迷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.28,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能 他剛剛不是跑在前面的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩一圈了 全力衝刺！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是芝村同學的請假單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.66,0:08:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過是不是寫錯了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休假的連絡地址跟家裏的不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是有她自己的理由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀧川 幫我拿一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己拿啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我再也動不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑操場50圈加單杠翻身500次 而且重複三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還加上青蛙跳跟仰臥起坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們根本就不是人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.74,0:09:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是受不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急廣播、緊急廣播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.38,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5121部隊所有男性請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請盡速前往校舍屋頂集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重複一次 請盡速前往校舍屋頂集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事情了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.26,0:09:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊們要幫你們～保～養～眼～睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.73,0:09:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還能動嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼啦 這到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.11,0:09:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借過借過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都來了還在發什麼呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕快來這裏坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 我想起來了 今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TAMAYA～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏天果然還是要這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未央、未央！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未央～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的衣服一模一樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟她一年前轉學過來時一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壬生屋是來遞補茜的缺額…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.09,0:11:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茜過世至今也一年了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年將會是她第一次的中元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.39,0:11:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茜過世至今也一年了呢
