Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.15,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預計熊本縣將會有豪雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位外出時不要忘記帶傘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本節目是由為人類開拓未來的芝村關係企業所提供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼那麼坐立不安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水…速水呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說他要到街上一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.81,0:16:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 原來速水不在的話 你就寂寞到食不下嚥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦 我才不管速水 問題是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是小舞也不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水那傢伙 難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.76,0:16:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為什麼會想到這種方向去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.69,0:16:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不純潔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們兩個完全沒有那種感覺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.56,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村說她要去車站一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車站？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.34,0:16:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您的特快車來回票跟床位券
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.07,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝您的惠顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放水燈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要幫去年過世的朋友過中元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.27,0:17:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以大家約好明天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村同學的老家在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是要探親對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天你有向芳野老師請假…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這跟你沒關係吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對、對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.73,0:18:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.47,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是汽油車 這是汽油車耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟這個比起來 電動車根本比芋頭還不如呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣啦 真不像話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.85,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來 這種VIP專用車怎麼會在我們學校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.86,0:18:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.29,0:18:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問是芝村舞小姐的同學嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問舞小姐人在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.30,0:19:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村她應該是坐昨天的夜車回老家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.24,0:19:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我隨時都有注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.71,0:19:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.22,0:19:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小舞該不會是富翁的千金吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更新更新！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說啊 芝村果然還是那個芝村集團吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.91,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年沒見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些就是全部了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.33,0:20:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護身符？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望小茜在天國不會害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茜她…會害怕？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.97,0:20:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.11,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,望望美我感覺得到 小茜她真的很害怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.68,0:20:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以了 她一定不會害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀧川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.67,0:20:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我有三長兩短的話 記得在水燈上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.21,0:20:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泡妞筆記本對吧 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我要汽油車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會沉下去吧 而且你又不能坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望不會再有人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望如此
