Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.21,0:22:31.51,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}隨著時代變動的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.01,0:22:37.58,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}即使迷失在困惑裏
